title: Maplesoft.Maple.17.02.x86.x64
description:
Maplesoft Maple 17.02, both 32 and 64 bits

Installing: Install either 32 bits or 64 bits (or both, that's possible if you have a 64 bits windows)

Choose single user licence  and  activate later during install. 

Then update to 17.02. Copy licence.dat to licence folder and maple.dll to the appropriate folder for your system (described in readme.txt). 

Restart your system. Done!

If you already have Maple 17 install you may download only the updates as all torrent files are in folders
